MOTORCYCLE INSURANCE

There for the Open Road
      





Feel the Freedom of Competitive Motorcycle Insurance
Talk to an agent or call 844-242-2554 today for a motorcycle insurance quote. Some companies charge extra for things like repairing/replacing protective gear, trip interruption costs if your motorcycle is damaged, or emergency roadside assistance. Not us. Plus, you'll have the got-your-back service of a State Farm™ agent whenever you need it.




Find an Agent







Or call 844-242-2554 for a quote.















Motorcycles Covered
State Farm offers affordable motorcycle insurance for two- and three-wheeled vehicles licensed for use on public roads, such as:

Factory-built motorcycles
Classic motorcycles
Custom motorcycles
Motor scooters
Minibikes
Trail bikes

Call 844-242-2554 today to get a motorcycle insurance quote, or contact your local agent.
 


What Does Motorcycle Insurance Cover?

Bodily injury to someone else or damage to someone else's property for which you are legally responsible while riding your motorcycle
Bodily injury to yourself because of an accident with an uninsured motorist
Damage to your motorcycle caused by an accident
Theft, fire, vandalism, and other losses — even while your motorcycle is in storage for the winter
Custom motorcycle work, such as paint or upgraded components
Attached side cars
Emergency roadside expenses
Damage to protective gear
Trip interruption expenses

 


Need a Motorcycle Loan?
Whether you need to finance two wheels or four, we've got you covered there too. State Farm Bank® offers competitive rates and no application fees.
 






